1
00:01:41,735 --> 00:01:45,072
Echigoya, you are quite an evil rascal!

2
00:01:45,072 --> 00:01:48,008
Omiya must be cursing your name
from the afterlife.

3
00:01:48,008 --> 00:01:49,343
Surely you just...

4
00:01:49,609 --> 00:01:53,747
You were the one who set up his murder
in the first place, Nezumiya, Sir.

5
00:01:53,880 --> 00:01:56,283
I mean, after all, that was you,
wasn't it?

6
00:01:56,283 --> 00:01:57,117
Really?

7
00:01:57,117 --> 00:01:58,552
Is that how it went?

8
00:01:58,552 --> 00:02:00,387
There you go, playing the innocent again!

9
00:02:19,473 --> 00:02:21,408
To our prosperous future!

10
00:02:24,211 --> 00:02:24,945
What is it?

11
00:02:24,945 --> 00:02:26,313
Is someone there?

12
00:02:28,749 --> 00:02:30,183
Who...
Who are you?

13
00:02:32,786 --> 00:02:37,324
Like the fading echo of a temple bell,
all things in life are temporary.

14
00:02:38,425 --> 00:02:41,061
The end of another day
marks the end

15
00:02:41,962 --> 00:02:44,765
