and his tyranny.

16
00:02:45,432 --> 00:02:46,466
Good evening.

17
00:02:46,800 --> 00:02:49,136
Sacchan, the assassin has come...

18
00:02:49,770 --> 00:02:51,638
Black market merchant Nezumiya...

19
00:02:51,905 --> 00:02:54,674
You preyed on the weak common folk
to line your own pockets.

20
00:02:54,674 --> 00:02:57,144
An act deserving of ten thousand deaths.

21
00:02:58,045 --> 00:03:00,547
I, assassin Sacchan,
shall bring you to justice!

22
00:03:01,148 --> 00:03:03,784
Hey, hey, hey,
I'm over here!

23
00:03:05,419 --> 00:03:06,987
Now, prepare to die, Nezumiya!

24
00:03:07,487 --> 00:03:09,389
What the hell did you come here for?

25
00:03:09,923 --> 00:03:11,124
Oh, I'm so sorry.

26
00:03:11,491 --> 00:03:13,760
But I seem to have dropped
my glasses earlier.

27
00:03:13,994 --> 00:03:15,996
Would you mind helping
me locate them?

28
00:03:16,396 --> 00:03:17,564
Here.

29
00:03:17,597 --> 00:03:18,832
Oh, thank you so much.

30
00:03:20,367 --> 00:03:22,502
