31
00:03:23,470 --> 00:03:24,871
being blind was better.

32
00:03:25,238 --> 00:03:26,640
Intruder!

33
00:03:30,043 --> 00:03:31,111
My plan has failed!

34
00:03:31,311 --> 00:03:32,279
Retreat!

35
00:03:32,512 --> 00:03:33,947
‐What?!
‐She's getting away!

36
00:03:34,147 --> 00:03:34,915
Hey!

37
00:03:34,915 --> 00:03:35,982
After her!

38
00:03:43,623 --> 00:03:44,691
I messed up.

39
00:03:45,025 --> 00:03:46,193
I have no choice.

40
00:03:46,193 --> 00:03:47,327
I'll return later.

41
00:04:01,842 --> 00:04:03,076
<i>Good morning!</i>

42
00:04:03,710 --> 00:04:05,278
Oh, Shinpachi, eh?

43
00:04:05,512 --> 00:04:06,446
