57
00:04:43,683 --> 00:04:46,219
They really are a bunch of slackers,
aren't they?

58
00:04:47,120 --> 00:04:50,056
Okay, time to get up.
It's morning.

59
00:04:50,657 --> 00:04:51,725
Hey, Gin!

60
