happened after I went drinking.

75
00:05:50,317 --> 00:05:53,253
Don't even try to play dumb
about the ninja cosplay part.

76
00:05:53,253 --> 00:05:54,354
Is she a ninja?

77
00:05:54,354 --> 00:05:55,822
