I'd pick a nurse costume!

81
00:06:00,860 --> 00:06:01,962
Are you telling the truth?

82
00:06:01,962 --> 00:06:03,230
Shinpachi...

83
00:06:03,663 --> 00:06:05,932
Men should have to mess around
while they're still young,

84
00:06:05,932 --> 00:06:07,300
because if they don't

85
00:06:07,300 --> 00:06:09,436
when they're older, they'll be
deceived by younger women,

86
00:06:09,436 --> 00:06:11,972
or become obsessed
with weird fantasies.

87
00:06:11,972 --> 00:06:13,506
