"husband and wife"?

102
00:06:48,275 --> 00:06:50,143
You will take responsibility,
won't you?

103
00:06:50,343 --> 00:06:51,645
After doing what you did.

104
00:06:51,645 --> 00:06:53,146
What do you mean "what I did"?

105
00:06:53,146 --> 00:06:55,048
I didn't even do anything,
you said so!

106
00:06:55,048 --> 00:06:56,283
What're you talking about?

107
00:06:56,283 --> 00:06:58,451
We were entwined together
just like this natto.

108
00:06:58,985 --> 00:06:59,953
It hurts!

109
00:07:00,186 --> 00:07:02,188
Like I said, that's not your mouth!

110
00:07:02,188 --> 00:07:05,425
Hey Gin, you can't change what you did.
Just accept it.

111
00:07:05,425 --> 00:07:07,827
Marriage is more about knowing
each other than love.

112
00:07:07,994 --> 00:07:09,629
What are you guys talking about?

113
00:07:09,629 --> 00:07:12,766
Your beloved Gin's about to be taken away
by some crazy natto girl!

114
00:07:12,966 --> 00:07:14,134
This is ridiculous!

115
00:07:14,134 --> 00:07:16,670
You're trying to trick me because
you know I don't remember anything!

116
00:07:17,103 --> 00:07:17,804
Right?

117
00:07:17,804 --> 00:07:19,105
To start with, we don't even
know each other's names,

118
00:07:19,105 --> 00:07:21,308
so how can we talk about marriage?

119
00:07:21,708 --> 00:07:25,312
You talk as if you don't remember
but your body cannot forget.

120
00:07:25,312 --> 00:07:27,514
Hey, will you stop talking like that!

121
00:07:27,514 --> 00:07:29,215
