Here!

124
00:07:34,454 --> 00:07:36,056
So, that's what happened.

125
00:07:36,056 --> 00:07:37,357
Well, my name is Sacchan.

126
00:07:37,357 --> 00:07:39,693
Please make me a happy wife,
my husband.

127
00:07:40,160 --> 00:07:41,094
I beg you.

128
00:07:41,661 --> 00:07:42,429
Likewise.

129
00:07:42,629 --> 00:07:43,897
Please be good to us, too.

130
00:07:44,097 --> 00:07:46,399
I like having fish over meat
for dinner, okay.

131
00:07:46,599 --> 00:07:48,435
Wait!
You're too quick to accept her in!

132
00:07:48,435 --> 00:07:49,936
And once again, I'm over here!

133
00:07:51,871 --> 00:07:53,640
<i>I'll lay low here for a while.</i>

134
00:07:53,907 --> 00:07:56,242
<i>This should give me enough time</i>
<i>to throw off my pursuers.</i>

135
00:08:15,662 --> 00:08:17,931
Looks like she's serious
about living here, huh?

136
00:08:17,931 --> 00:08:19,733
What are you going to do then, Gin?

137
00:08:19,833 --> 00:08:24,070
A serious woman like her is harder to get
rid of than the stinking smell of durians.

138
00:08:24,070 --> 00:08:25,338
Oh, good grief.

139
00:08:25,972 --> 00:08:29,642
In times like this, all I can do is calm
myself down with something sweet.

140
00:08:30,844 --> 00:08:33,313
<i>He simply listens to whatever I say.</i>

141
00:08:33,313 --> 00:08:35,048
<i>Men are such stupid creatures right?</i>

142
00:08:35,181 --> 00:08:38,718
<i>All</i> <i>I</i> <i>have</i> <i>to</i> <i>do</i> <i>now</i> <i>is</i> <i>play</i> <i>the</i> <i>part</i>
<i>of</i> <i>the</i> <i>cute,</i> <i>obedient,</i> <i>young</i> <i>wife.</i>

143
00:08:39,886 --> 00:08:43,056
Hey, has anyone seen the pudding
that I put in the fridge?

144
00:08:46,259 --> 00:08:48,361
Hey, there was some pudding
in the fridge.

145
00:08:48,862 --> 00:08:49,963
Oh come on!

146
00:08:50,263 --> 00:08:51,865
And I tried to hide it, too!

147
00:08:51,965 --> 00:08:54,167
I guess I have no choice,
you little piggy!

148
00:08:55,135 --> 00:08:56,636
What day is it today?

149
00:08:57,203 --> 00:08:59,072
What is it?
Garbage day?

150
00:08:59,339 --> 00:09:01,041
The expiration date on some food?

151
00:09:01,041 --> 00:09:02,909
Oh my, you forgot?

152
00:09:03,209 --> 00:09:05,879
It's the anniversary of when you
and I started going out!

153
00:09:05,879 --> 00:09:07,480
But we just met a little while ago.

154
00:09:07,480 --> 00:09:10,383
Plus, didn't your personality
just change or something?

155
00:09:10,517 --> 00:09:11,785
Ta‐da!

156
00:09:11,785 --> 00:09:13,953
Natto pudding for our anniversary!

157
00:09:15,822 --> 00:09:17,690
Am I being punished for something?

158
00:09:18,258 --> 00:09:21,928
Today, I've made a very special
combination of our two favorite things.

159
00:09:22,328 --> 00:09:24,364
And now, open up.

160
00:09:25,131 --> 00:09:26,866
Enough of this already!

161
00:09:30,003 --> 00:09:32,372
You, after pushing yourself
on me as my wife,

162
00:09:32,372 --> 00:09:34,774
you're going to harass my precious
pudding too?

163
00:09:35,375 --> 00:09:37,444
The hierarchy in this
household starts with me.

164
00:09:37,710 --> 00:09:38,978
And after that, it's sweets.

165
00:09:38,978 --> 00:09:39,846
You understand me?

166
00:09:39,846 --> 00:09:42,382
Hey!
Sweets are number two over us?

167
00:09:44,784 --> 00:09:46,419
<i>I didn't play my hand right.</i>

168
00:09:47,120 --> 00:09:48,088
<i>Bear it.</i>

169
00:09:48,321 --> 00:09:49,389
<i>Bear it, Sacchan.</i>

170
00:09:54,294 --> 00:09:55,662
You don't have to be shy about it.

171
00:09:56,029 --> 00:09:57,197
Now eat some!

172
00:09:57,464 --> 00:09:58,731
Like hell I'm eating this!

173
00:09:59,332 --> 00:10:01,568
It's okay.
This is actually pretty good.

174
00:10:01,568 --> 00:10:03,236
Hey, Kagura, don't eat that!

175
00:10:03,837 --> 00:10:06,806
You're not going to eat it, so don't try
to create some kind of collaboration

176
00:10:06,806 --> 00:10:08,708
between pudding and natto, moron!

177
00:10:08,975 --> 00:10:10,076
Are you trying to be a producer?

178
00:10:10,076 --> 00:10:11,744
I'll whack your head with a megaphone!

179
00:10:12,879 --> 00:10:14,514
‐I can't believe how disgusting that is.
<i>‐This is humiliating.</i>

180
00:10:14,514 --> 00:10:16,916
‐I want my sweets, not natto.
<i>‐I was once one of the elite spy agent,</i>

181
00:10:16,916 --> 00:10:18,284
‐Who would mix the two, anyway!
<i>‐why should I be subjected to</i>

182
00:10:18,284 --> 00:10:19,752
