184
00:10:20,553 --> 00:10:23,957
Hey, if you can't abide by these rules,
then get out, you worthless idiot!

185
00:10:25,625 --> 00:10:26,426
<i>But what is this?</i>

186
00:10:26,426 --> 00:10:27,660
<i>What is this feeling?</i>

187
00:10:28,061 --> 00:10:29,062
