something sweet.

189
00:10:31,397 --> 00:10:32,432
Wait up!

190
00:10:33,166 --> 00:10:34,133
Seriously.

191
00:10:34,133 --> 00:10:35,635
How the hell did you end up like that?

192
00:10:35,635 --> 00:10:38,071
Help me!
I'm trapped in natto!

193
00:10:40,540 --> 00:10:41,708
Why are you following me?

194
00:10:42,142 --> 00:10:43,510
And what's up with that outfit?

195
00:10:44,210 --> 00:10:46,479
Don't you like my old fashioned good
housewife look?

196
00:10:46,679 --> 00:10:48,448
You wanna play the typical
husband and wife game?

197
00:10:48,448 --> 00:10:51,184
Then I'll play a jobless husband
who forgets to take out the trash.

198
00:10:51,551 --> 00:10:52,785
That's not a typical husband!

199
00:10:53,686 --> 00:10:56,589
<i>My</i> <i>pursuers</i> <i>won't</i> <i>recognize</i> <i>me</i>
<i>at</i> <i>all</i> <i>in</i> <i>this</i> <i>disguise.</i>

200
00:10:56,890 --> 00:11:00,159
<i>Now all I have to do is play the part</i>
<i>of the cute, obedient, young wife.</i>

201
00:11:00,894 --> 00:11:01,728
What's the matter?

202
00:11:02,262 --> 00:11:03,496
Nothing at all.

203
00:11:05,565 --> 00:11:06,266
Hey!

204
00:11:06,266 --> 00:11:08,568
You were looking at that
woman just now, weren't you?

205
00:11:08,735 --> 00:11:10,770
I want you to tell me now,
is she your type?

206
00:11:11,037 --> 00:11:12,672
Absolutely not, moron!

207
00:11:12,672 --> 00:11:15,175
Are you trying to make me out
to be a weirdo, or something?

208
00:11:15,475 --> 00:11:17,544
What in the world are you
doing out here?

209
00:11:18,144 --> 00:11:19,279
And who might you be?

210
00:11:19,679 --> 00:11:20,747
Who might I be?

211
00:11:21,047 --> 00:11:22,649
I should ask you who you are?

212
00:11:23,116 --> 00:11:24,117
Gintoki?

213
00:11:24,117 --> 00:11:26,185
You just called him "Gintoki".

214
00:11:26,553 --> 00:11:27,620
It's not a big deal.

215
00:11:28,021 --> 00:11:31,891
By the way, Gintoki, you said that by
today, you'd pay me the last month's...

216
00:11:32,091 --> 00:11:32,859
