222
00:11:46,706 --> 00:11:48,207
You already had your fun with him!

223
00:11:48,608 --> 00:11:50,009
You don't deserve any money!

224
00:11:50,310 --> 00:11:52,312
What on earth is that girl talking about?

225
00:11:52,645 --> 00:11:54,414
You're nothing but an old flame.

226
00:11:54,414 --> 00:11:56,716
‐Go drown yourself in your old memories.
‐Hey!

227
00:11:56,716 --> 00:11:58,885
You really think this
is my ex‐girlfriend?

228
00:11:58,885 --> 00:12:01,120
Then you must think that
I'm a weirdo among weirdos!

229
00:12:01,387 --> 00:12:03,356
Listen, I'm going to kick
both of your asses!

230
00:12:04,390 --> 00:12:05,959
Don't tell me
she's your mother?

231
00:12:06,225 --> 00:12:07,260
Is she your mother?

232
00:12:07,460 --> 00:12:10,363
Hey, if my mother were like this,
I'd get a big tattoo on my forehead

233
00:12:10,363 --> 00:12:12,198
