put me out of my misery!

234
00:12:12,365 --> 00:12:14,300
Do you want me to shoot
you right here and now?

235
00:12:15,768 --> 00:12:17,704
For everything rude I've done,
please forgive me...

236
00:12:18,137 --> 00:12:19,105
