chasing a stray cat

240
00:12:24,577 --> 00:12:25,745
that ran off with a fish.

241
00:12:26,079 --> 00:12:28,982
She's a little bit of an airhead and
likes to cosplay as a random wife.

242
00:12:29,248 --> 00:12:30,617
<i>To be treated this rudely...</i>

243
00:12:30,917 --> 00:12:32,485
